data.description: Step into your charming one-story haven where thoughtful renovations and cozy features await. The heart of this home is the inviting living area, complete with a warm fireplace that adds a touch of comfort and ambiance to your space. As you explore further, you'll appreciate the continuity of laminate flooring throughout, creating a seamless flow and adding a modern touch to each room. The kitchen has undergone a tasteful renovation, featuring sleek granite countertops, contemporary cabinets and matching stainless steel appliances. With a renovated kitchen and bathrooms, this home is a perfect blend of comfort and style, inviting you to create lasting memories in every corner. Schedule a showing today and discover the charm and sophistication of this beautifully updated residence.
